  "title": "Deputy General Manager",
  "description": "<h2>Deputy General Manager / Vice President – Singapore Branch</h2><p>(Vacuum Piping / Pumping Line - Semiconductor)<br /></p><h3><strong>Job Summary</strong></h3><p>This senior management role at the Singapore Branch offers long-term career development and equity participation opportunities. You will lead and coordinate on-site vacuum piping and pumping line projects within the semiconductor industry, driving operational excellence and team performance.</p><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Lead and coordinate on-site vacuum piping and pumping line installation projects to ensure timely and quality delivery within the semiconductor environment</li><li>Manage and develop on-site work teams to optimize productivity and maintain high safety and quality standards</li><li>Apply expert knowledge of vacuum piping systems to troubleshoot and resolve technical challenges on-site</li><li>Communicate effectively with cross-functional teams and stakeholders to align project goals and progress</li><li>Demonstrate strong ownership and accountability to meet project milestones and company objectives</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Detail-oriented, strong sense of responsibility, and proven management capability</li><li>Strong ability to lead, coordinate, and manage on-site work teams</li><li>Highly experienced in on-site vacuum piping (Pumping Line) semiconductor works</li><li>Good communication skills</li></ul><h3><strong>Salary Package</strong></h3><ul><li>Final package to be discussed during the interview, based on experience and capability</li><li>Equity participation granted upon successful completion of probation period, applicable to Headquarters and/or Singapore Branch</li></ul><h3><strong>Work Location</strong></h3><p>East Singapore, Semiconductor company</p><p>_________________________________________</p><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified. </em><br /></p><p>i-Link Manpower Consultancy Pte. Ltd. | 21C0445</p><p>Kristy Y.P.L. | R23118792</p>",
